<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
    .form-container{
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background-image: url("../img/bg.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        padding: 0 16rem;
    }
    *{
        font-family: sans-serif;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .inner-container{
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .title{
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        /* align-items: center; */
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .inner-container > div{
        width: 50%;
    }
    .logo{
        background: linear-gradient(105deg,#ffe200 20%,#ffe20000 62%);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding: 3px 20px;
        width: 100%;
    }
    .logo > img{
        height: 52px;
        object-fit: contain;
        width: 75px;
    }
    .textArea h2{
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-weight: bolder;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        margin-top: 13px;
        color: #fff;
    }
    .textArea p{
        color: #fff;
    }
    .inner-form > div{
        width: 70%;
        height: fit-content;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 1.6rem;
    }
    .inner-form > div > h1{
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #FF0000;
    }
    .inner-form > div > p{
        font-size: .7rem;
    }
    .inner-form{
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: end;
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .pinInput{
        background: #E8E8E8 0% 0% no-repeat padding-box;
        border-radius: 20px;
        opacity: 1;
        width: 100%;
        height: 30px;
        border: none;
        margin-top: 1.4rem;
        outline: none;
        padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    .sub-btn{
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: end;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .sub-btn > button{
        padding: .4rem 1.1rem;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #ffe200;
        color: #000;
        font-weight: bold;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
</style>
<body>
    <form class="form-container" action="/backToVerify" method="POST">
        <div class="inner-container">
            <div class="title">
                <div class="logo">
                    <img src="/img/dark.png" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="textArea">
                    <h2>It's just so nippy!</h2>
                    <p>Where cargo security and user satisfaction meet.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="inner-form">
                <div>
                    <h1>PIN Incorrect</h1>
                    <p>Please check the PIN and try again, if the PIN is incorrect, please do not hand over your cargo, contact the <a style="text-decoration: none;color: #0000FF;" href="mailto:support@zipi.co.za">Zipi Support</a> team and we will be able to assist you.</p>
                    <div class="sub-btn">
                        <button>Try again</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>